#: ../../talk/matterbridge.rst:2
msgid "Matterbridge"
msgstr "Droichead an Mháthair"

#: ../../talk/matterbridge.rst:6
msgid ""
"Matterbridge integration in Nextcloud Talk makes it possible to create "
"'bridges' between Talk conversations and conversations on other chat "
"services like MS Teams, Discord, Matrix and others. You can find a list of "
"supported protocols `on the Matterbridge github page. "
"<https://github.com/42wim/matterbridge#features>`_"
msgstr ""
"A bhuí le comhtháthú Matterbridge i Nextcloud Talk, is féidir 'droichid' a "
"chruthú idir comhráite Talk agus comhráite ar sheirbhísí comhrá eile ar nós "
"MS Teams, Discord, Matrix agus eile. Is féidir leat liosta de na prótacail a"
" dtacaítear leo a fháil ar leathanach github Matterbridge. "
"<https://github.com/42wim/matterbridge#features>`_"

#: ../../talk/matterbridge.rst:8
msgid ""
"A moderator can add a Matterbridge connection in the chat conversation "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le modhnóir nasc Matterbridge a chur leis i socruithe an chomhrá."

#: ../../talk/matterbridge.rst:13
msgid ""
"Each bridge has its own configuration requirements. Information for most is "
"available on the Matterbridge wiki and can be accessed behind ``more "
"information`` menu in the ``...`` menu. You can also `access the wiki "
"directly. <https://github.com/42wim/matterbridge/wiki>`_"
msgstr ""
"Tá a riachtanais chumraíochta féin ag gach droichead. Tá faisnéis faoin "
"gcuid is mó ar fáil ar vicí Matterbridge agus is féidir rochtain a fháil "
"uirthi taobh thiar den roghchlár ``tuilleadh eolais`` sa roghchlár ``...``. "
"Is féidir leat `rochtain dhíreach a fháil ar an vicí freisin. "
"<https://github.com/42wim/matterbridge/wiki>`_"
